{"word":"G1206 - δευτεραῖος - deuteraîos - dyoo-ter-ah'-yos - Next day","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δευτεραῖος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">deuteraîos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dyoo-ter-ah'-yos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Next day</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இரண்டாம் நாள் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of or belonging to the second; on the second day"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1208 - δεύτερος - deúteros - dyoo'-ter-os/1208\">G1208</a>; <i>secondary</i>, that is, (specifically) on the <i>second</i> day: - next day.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}